parameters:
Memimi: Ugh... The convenience store's promotional account
is completely on fire... I wish they would stop uploading
images... Maybe it's better to delete the account... after
all the effort to keep it going...
Memimi: Ah, a message... There are so many...

"Congratulations on your AV debut, Memimi-chan!! Seeing you
drink semen with that erotic face was the best!! You're more
suited for this than being a convenience store clerk!!"

"I used to be healed by your cute photos, but to think you
were a bitch who sleeps with anyone, I'm so disillusioned. I
respected you, but you turned out to be that kind of person.
I'm blocking you now, goodbye. P.S. I won't watch it, but if
you're doing AV, you should do a uniform situation. I won't
watch it though."

"I recorded myself masturbating to Memimi-chan's gangbang
video!! You can masturbate to this too, Memimi-chan!! When
you do, please take a video and send it to me ^ ^ Next time
let's masturbate together over a video call ^ ^"

Memimi: Oh no... the mental damage... I can't take it
anymore... I have no choice but to abandon this account...

Memimi: Again... I won't look anymore... It's bound to be
disgusting content... Ugh...

Memimi: Huh... that icon! It's... Bunny-chan!! Bunny-chan
sent me a message!

"Memimi-chan, are you okay? We, the anti-mayor monsters,
have gathered and are hiding in a bar in the underground
city. Shark Broccoli-san is with us."

"Don't worry about us here, please escape quickly. According
to Shark Broccoli-san, there's a hole in the back wall of
the employee changing room that's only covered with
wallpaper because there's no budget to fix it. The space
under the floor leads directly to the underground city, and
you can move without being seen by anyone."

Memimi: Oh... the great leader is safe too...! Thank
goodness... even a path for escape... what a magnificent
person...

Drillmaid: ...I see, everyone's at the bar... A hole in the
wall of the employee changing room... Hmm...

Memimi: No, it's not like that... I mean, it's different...
No, ugh... I can't hide it anymore... I have no choice but
to silence you... Prepare yourself, you...!

Drillmaid: ...It's fine, go on... Hurry up and escape.
Before the next shoot starts.

Drillmaid: Orca Mayor too... he wasn't always like that...
He was a star wrestler in a costume wrestling organization,
kind and a good person. But after the organization went
bankrupt due to debt, he became like that.

Drillmaid: He admired Shark Broccoli's older brother... You
resemble him a lot. I don't want to see him destroy his own
memories anymore...

Memimi: ...Another reason has emerged for me to defeat him.
Wait for me, when the time comes for a rematch, I will break
that arrogant nose of his and turn him back into the
pathetic old man he was!

Drillmaid: Well, it's not like he was originally a pathetic
old man but... If you're going, take this too. It arrived
while you were asleep.

Memimi: The Shark Mask... it's been repaired! With this, I
have the strength of a hundred men, I will surely win!!
Thank you for everything, Drillmaid... I will definitely
repay this favor!

Drillmaid: Getting all excited, geez... I'm not expecting
much but I'll be rooting for you, Duke Shark...
Memimi has escaped to the city...!
"Formation of the Resistance!? The Journey to\nthe Bar Volume"
"Let's meet up with the big bosses at the bar!"
"Duke Shark lost for real? AV debut confirmed then!!"

"Shark Broccoli is also missing, and the organization is
almost annihilated. Other organizations seem to be
disbanding one after another as if they think this is the
right time. By the way, has anyone seen Bunny-chan after the
match?"

"Mud Profit City is over... There really is no one who can
beat the mayor."
The voices of despair from the citizens can be heard...

The Monster Fight headquarters seems to have closed down
their homepage... Instead, there are advertising banners
posted by Orca Broccoli Mayor...

The Monster Fight headquarters seems to have closed down
their homepage... Instead, there are advertising banners
posted by Orca Broccoli Mayor...
"Grand Campaign! The Tale of the Citizen's Sex\nSlave"
"Let's listen to what everyone has to say! If\nwe get tired, let's take a break on the\ninternet!"

Memimi: Have I been defeated...? Despite losing, there's no
pain in my body, no injuries... Perhaps they didn't want to
decrease my market value...

Drillmaid: Drilliiing! That's right!! From today on, you're
the mayor's exclusive AV actress! You'll obey any lewd
orders, and everything will be filmed and streamed live!

Drillmaid: Well, since I'm a woman, I won't lust after
you... but I do feel sympathy. I never thought Lord Shark
Broccoli would go back on his promise... but no matter what
happens, don't you dare refuse or resist, got it?

Having been defeated by Mayor Orca Asparagus, Memimi must
now comply with the mayor's sexual commands... The situation
is probably already known throughout the city. Outside the
room awaits a world worse than Memimi can even imagine...

Drillmaid: ...So you've lost, huh. Well, I figured it was
impossible. The mayor won't show any mercy now... brace
yourself.

Memimi: Having lost, I will obey the orders... I'll work
twice as hard for Shark Broccoli-sama, our great leader. It
will be unimaginably tough... but I am prepared...

Drillmaid: Even if you can't walk around as the noble Shark
anymore, don't be too pessimistic. Just debut as a different
monster! If you wear a costume-type monster suit, you can
hide your face.

Memimi: It's a forceful approach, but quite intriguing... I
have no intention whatsoever of abandoning my role as the
noble Shark, bestowed upon me by Shark Broccoli-sama...

Drillmaid: Heh heh, did you know I'm also a designer of
monster suits? I designed this body myself.

Drillmaid: The three monsters that were born five years ago
and became the basis for all the monsters in the city...
Shark Broccoli, Orca Asparagus, and me, Drillmaid... all my
designs!
Memimi: Is that so... That's quite... impressive, senpai...

Drillmaid: The legendary designer that I am will think up a
new monster suit for you! Just wait a moment...
Memimi: No... well, I don't really need a new design...

Drillmaid: Done... how about this!? "Sea Urchin Tango"!!
This guy looks strong, doesn't he...? It's a design to be
proud of...!
Memimi: What am I supposed to say to that...

Drillmaid: Looks like you've been through some rough stuff!
Well... uh... hang in there...

Memimi: Don't pity me... ugh, it's no use... my spirit is...
broken...

Shark Broccoli-Mayor: Sha-sha-sha~!! The streaming views
were incredible, but the sales of the edited videos are off
the charts too!! Not just domestically, but the overseas
access is crazy!!

Shark Broccoli-Mayor: There's a bunch of people posting
their thoughts on social media too, and it's going to keep
spreading!! Congratulations, you've become the world's most
famous AV actress!

Memimi: ...Is it... really true? Did you really... upload it
to the net...? My... being violated... my disgraceful crying
and screaming... exposed to the public...

Shark Broccoli-Mayor: If you're curious, just search it on
the computer behind you! You can see the view count too... I
think it was about 60 million views now? Since the operation
is overseas, we uploaded it uncensored, sha-sha-sha-sha-
sha...

Shark Broccoli-Mayor: Once your strength has recovered, come
outside! We've got a pile of AV projects waiting for you...
I'm so excited! Wonder how many hundreds of millions we can
make... I can't stop drooling!

Memimi: It's all over... ah... I stood my ground, but in the
end, I've fallen to rock bottom... heh... heheh, hehehe...

Drillmaid: I'm not saying this to be mean, but apologize to
Shark Broccoli-Mayor and get his forgiveness... If you find
the escaped Shark and get the recipe for that delicious
powder, you should be able to quit being an AV actress...

Memimi: ...If it comes to that, I'd rather stay an AV
actress... It's hard and unbearable but... I can't betray
Shark Broccoli-Boss... *sniffle*... I must... accept the
humiliation after all... *sob*...

Unable to escape or submit, Memimi could only cry and
endure...
